### Audit Logging API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = YOUR_USER_ID_HERE
@auditLogId = YOUR_AUDIT_LOG_ID_HERE

### ==============================================
### USER ROUTES (Authenticated)
### ==============================================

### 1. Get My Activity
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/my-activity?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Get My Activity with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/my-activity?startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&endDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Get My Login History
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/my-login-history?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Get User Activity (Own)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/user/{{userId}}?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### ADMIN ROUTES
### ==============================================

### 5. List All Audit Logs (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. List Audit Logs with Filters (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?action=USER_LOGIN&success=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. List Failed Operations (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?success=false&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. List Document Operations (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?resource=DOCUMENT&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. List by Specific User (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?userId={{userId}}&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10. List by IP Address (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin?ipAddress=192.168&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 11. Get Audit Log by ID (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/{{auditLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 12. Get Audit Statistics (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13. Get Audit Statistics with Date Range (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/stats?startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&endDate=2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14. Get Activity Timeline (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/timeline?groupBy=day
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 15. Get Activity Timeline by Week (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/timeline?groupBy=week&startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 16. Get Recent Activity (Admin Dashboard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/recent?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 17. Get Suspicious Activities (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/suspicious?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 18. Export Audit Logs as JSON (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/export?format=json&startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 19. Export Audit Logs as CSV (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/export?format=csv&startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20. Export Filtered Logs (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/admin/export?format=json&action=DOCUMENT_UPLOAD&resource=DOCUMENT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### CURL Examples
### ==============================================

# Get My Activity
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/my-activity?page=1&limit=20" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# Get My Login History
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/my-login-history?limit=10" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# List All Audit Logs (Admin)
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/admin?page=1&limit=20" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Get Audit Statistics (Admin)
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/admin/stats" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Get Suspicious Activities (Admin)
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/admin/suspicious?limit=20" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Export as CSV (Admin)
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/audit/admin/export?format=csv" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN" \
#   -o audit-logs.csv
